#: ../../../release_details/9.6/fix-EGL-warning.md:1
msgid "Fix harmless EGL render window initialization warning"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.6/fix-EGL-warning.md:3
msgid ""
"VTK now removes unused OpenGL point sprite enabling code from the EGL render "
"window initialization. Point sprites are available by default in core OpenGL "
"profiles and do not require explicit enabling. This removes a harmless "
"warning during window setup on some systems."
msgstr ""
